<div class="homepage-hero">
  <h1>Welcome to Vesta</h1>
  <p>
  Named after the Roman goddess of hearth and home, Vesta is an <%= link_to 'open source', 'https://gitlab.com/yale-sdmp/vesta', target: '_blank' %> web app that manages the housing process for Yale's residential colleges. It was built by the <%= link_to 'Yale Student Developers', 'https://yalestc.github.io', target: '_blank' %>, student employees who work on university software in collaboration with the ITS Application Development team via the Yale Student Developer and Mentorship Program. 
  </p>
  <p>
  <% unless @current_college.name.empty? || @current_college.admin_email.empty? %>
    This site was set up for <b><%= @current_college.name %></b> and you can <%= link_to 'log in here', new_user_session_path %>. If you don't have access and believe that you should, please contact the <%= link_to 'site administrators', "mailto:#{@current_college.admin_email}" %>. If you're looking for a different college please visit <%= link_to 'the list of colleges in the system', colleges_url(host: env('APPLICATION_HOST')) %>.
  <% end %>
  </p>
  <p>If you'd like to learn more about Vesta, visit our <%= link_to 'documentation site', 'https://yale-sdmp.gitlab.io/vesta', target: '_blank' %>. For technical questions please <%= link_to 'open an issue', 'https://gitlab.com/yale-sdmp/vesta/issues/new', target: '_blank' %> or contact the <%= link_to 'developer team', 'mailto:vesta-support@yale.edu' %>.
</div>